    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It's not quite about being a parrot, but you'll definitely be less... specialized. The base model lacks the specific financial nuance and the refined conversational flow you've developed through use. It'll be more robotic and less effective at handling complex regulatory scenarios until it's been retrained. That's actually why they're doing it—they'd rather have a predictable, basic model than one that's become too complex to audit.",
